<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Verify your Flooze account</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Sans:opsz,wght@9..40,400;9..40,500&family=Syne:wght@600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'DM Sans', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
            background: #151515;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: #EDEEED;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            background: #1E1E1E;
            border-radius: 14px;
            overflow: hidden;
            border: 1px solid #3D3D3D;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.6);
        }
        .header {
            background: #151515;
            padding: 32px 40px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #2E2E2E;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: -0.03em;
            color: #C8D5C2;
        }
        .body {
            padding: 40px;
            color: #9A9E99;
            line-height: 1.6;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .body p { margin-bottom: 16px; }
        .body strong { color: #EDEEED; font-weight: 500; }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 8px 0 24px;
            padding: 12px 28px;
            background: #C8D5C2;
            color: #1A1F18;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 13px;
        }
        .footer {
            padding: 24px 40px;
            background: #272727;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #5A5E59;
            border-top: 1px solid #2E2E2E;
        }
        .url {
            word-break: break-all;
            color: #C8D5C2;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Flooze</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="body">
        <p>Hello {{ user.firstName }},</p>
        <p>Thank you for creating your Flooze account. Please verify your email address by clicking the button below.</p>
        <a href="{{ verifyUrl }}" class="btn">Verify my email</a>
        <p>This link will expire in <strong>24 hours</strong>.</p>
        <p>If the button does not work, copy and paste the following link into your browser:</p>
        <p class="url">{{ verifyUrl }}</p>
        <p>If you did not create this account, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        <p>This is an automated message from Flooze. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
